{"title_page": "Maxim Fedin", "text_new": "{{short description|Kazakh football midfielder|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Maxim Fedin\n| image = [[File:M fedin against russia.png|200px]]\n| fullname = Maxim Fedin\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1996|06|08|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Kazakhstan]]\n| height = 1.67 m\n| position = [[Midfielder#Attacking midfielder|Attacking midfielder]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.novosti.rs/vesti/sport.294.html:530639-Fedin-Spartak-idealna-odskocna-daska|title=Fedin: Spartak idealna odsko\u010dna daska|website=[[Ve\u010dernje novosti]]|language=Serbian|date=25 January 2015|accessdate=23 August 2015}}</ref> / [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub = [[Kaysar]]\n| clubnumber = 96\n| youthyears1 = \n| youthclubs1 = [[FC Irtysh Pavlodar|Irtysh Pavlodar]]\n| years1 = 2014\n| clubs1 = [[FC Bayterek|Bayterek]]\n| caps1 = 26\n| goals1 = 3\n| years2 = 2015\u20132016\n| clubs2 = [[FK Spartak Subotica|Spartak Subotica]]\n| caps2 = 5\n| goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2016\n| clubs3 = [[FC Atyrau|Atyrau]]\n| caps3 = 13\n| goals3 = 1\n| years4 = 2017\n| clubs4 = [[FC Okzhetpes|Okzhetpes]]\n| caps4 = 26\n| goals4 = 2\n| years5 = 2018\u2013\n| clubs5 = [[FC Tobol|Tobol]]\n| caps5 = 61\n| goals5 = 7\n| nationalyears1 = 2012\n| nationalteam1 = [[Kazakhstan national under-17 football team|Kazakhstan U17]]\n| nationalcaps1 = 6\n| nationalgoals1 = 1\n| nationalyears2 = 2014\n| nationalteam2 = [[Kazakhstan national under-19 football team|Kazakhstan U19]]\n| nationalcaps2 = 3\n| nationalgoals2 = 0\n| nationalyears3 = 2015\u2013\n| nationalteam3 = [[Kazakhstan national under-21 football team|Kazakhstan U21]]\n| nationalcaps3 = 16\n| nationalgoals3 = 2\n| nationalyears4 = 2018\u2013\n| nationalteam4 = [[Kazakhstan national football team|Kazakhstan]]\n| nationalcaps4 = 13\n| nationalgoals4 = 1\n| pcupdate = {{date|2019-11-10}}\n| ntupdate = 19 November 2019\n}}\n\n'''Maxim Fedin''' ({{lang-kk|\u041c\u0430\u043a\u0441\u0438\u043c \u0424\u0435\u0434\u0438\u043d}}, born 8 June 1996) is a [[Kazakhstan|Kazakh]] [[Association football|football]] [[midfielder]] who plays for [[FC Tobol]] in the [[Kazakhstan Premier League]].\n\n==Career==\n===Club===\n====Bayterek Astana====\nFedin passed the youth school of [[FC Irtysh Pavlodar|Irtysh Pavlodar]]. For the [[2014 Kazakhstan First Division|2014]] season, he made 26 appearances and scored 3 goals, playing with [[FC Bayterek|Bayterek]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gradsubotica.co.rs/spartak-potpisao-kazahstanac-maksim-fedin/|title=Spartak: Potpisao Kazahstanac Maksim Fedin|website=gradsubotica.co.rs|language=Serbian|date=26 January 2015|accessdate=23 August 2015}}</ref>\n\n====Spartak Subotica====\nFedin joined [[FK Spartak Subotica|Spartak Subotica]] in January 2015, but he could not playing until the end of [[2014\u201315 Serbian SuperLiga|2014\u201315]] season, because of injury.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sports.kz/news/maksim-fedin-v-baytereke-ya-priobrel-neobhodimyiy-dlya-vyistupleniy-za-rubejom-opyit|title=\u041c\u0430\u043a\u0441\u0438\u043c \u0424\u0435\u0434\u0438\u043d: \"\u0412 \"\u0411\u0430\u0439\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0435\u043a\u0435\" \u044f \u043f\u0440\u0438\u043e\u0431\u0440\u0435\u043b \u043d\u0435\u043e\u0431\u0445\u043e\u0434\u0438\u043c\u044b\u0439 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0432\u044b\u0441\u0442\u0443\u043f\u043b\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u0437\u0430 \u0440\u0443\u0431\u0435\u0436\u043e\u043c \u043e\u043f\u044b\u0442\"|website=sports.kz|language=Kazakh|date=14 May 2015|accessdate=23 August 2015}}</ref> He made his [[Serbian SuperLiga|SuperLiga]] debut in the 7th fixture of [[2015\u201316 Serbian SuperLiga|2015\u201316]] season, against [[FK Metalac Gornji Milanovac|Metalac]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.superliga.rs/index.php/izvestaji-2015-16/2863-7-kolo-spartak-metalac#.Vdkm-iV_OqY|title=7.Kolo: Spartak - Metalac|website=Serbian SuperLiga official website|language=Serbian|date=22 August 2015|accessdate=23 August 2015}}</ref>\n\n====Atyrau====\nOn 9 July 2016, Fedin signed for [[Kazakhstan Premier League]] side [[FC Atyrau]].<ref>{{cite web|title=\u0424\u0435\u0434\u0438\u043d \u2013 \u043d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447\u043e\u043a \u0410\u0442\u044b\u0440\u0430\u0443|url=http://www.rfcatyrau.kz/rus/news/1466|website=rfcatyrau.kz|publisher=FC Atyrau|accessdate=9 July 2016|language=Russian|date=9 July 2016}}</ref>\n\n====Okzhetpes====\nOn 12 January 2017, Fedin signed a one-year contract with [[FC Okzhetpes]].<ref>{{cite web|title=\u0424\u0435\u0434\u0438\u043d \u2013 \u0438\u0433\u0440\u043e\u043a \u0424\u041a \u041e\u043a\u0436\u0435\u0442\u043f\u0435\u0441|url=http://www.okzhetpes.kz/ru/news/fedin-igrok-fk-okzhetpes|website=okzhetpes.kz/|publisher=FC Okzhetpes|accessdate=12 January 2017|language=Russian|date=12 January 2017}}</ref>\n\n====Tobol====\nOn 25 December 2018, [[FC Tobol]] announced the siging of Fedin,<ref>{{cite web|title=\u041d\u0438\u043a\u043e\u043b\u0430\u0439 \u041f\u0430\u043d\u0438\u043d: \u00ab\u0422\u043e\u0431\u043e\u043b\u00bb \u0433\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0432 \u043a \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0432\u044b\u043c \u0441\u0431\u043e\u0440\u0430\u043c \u2014 \u0441\u043e\u0445\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u043a\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044f\u043a, \u0441\u0444\u043e\u0440\u043c\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043b\u0438 \u0442\u0440\u0435\u043d\u0435\u0440\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u0448\u0442\u0430\u0431|url=https://fctobol.kz/nikolaj-panin-tobol-gotov-k-pervym-sboram-sohranili-kostyak-sformirovali-trenerskij-shtab/|website=fctobol.kz|publisher=FC Tobol|accessdate=5 July 2018|language=Russian|date=25 December 2017}}</ref> with Fedin extending his contract with Tobol until the end of 2020 on 31 December 2019.<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0424\u0435\u0434\u0438\u043d \u0441 \u043d\u0430\u043c\u0438! |url=https://fctobol.kz/fedin-s-nami/ |website=fctobol.kz/ |publisher=FC Tobol |accessdate=5 January 2020 |language=Russian |date=31 December 2019}}</ref>\n\n===International===\nMaxim Fedin was a regular member of all youth sections of the Kazakh national team, namely the [[Kazakhstan national under-17 football team|U17]], [[Kazakhstan national under-19 football team|U19]] and [[Kazakhstan national under-21 football team|U21]]. On June 10, 2017, he was part of the [[Kazakhstan national football team]] in a qualifying game for the 2018 FIFA World Cup against Denmark, but ended being an unused substitute.<ref>{{Soccerway|maxim-fedin/273270}}</ref> He received a new call for the friendly game against Azerbaijan played on June 5, 2018,<ref>[http://www.kff.kz/news/view/1527528089- KAZAKHSTAN NATIONAL TEAM SQUAD FOR MATCH WITH AZERBAIJAN] at KFF.kz, retrieved 5-6-2018</ref> but again failed to debut. He made his debut for the senior squad on 13 October 2018 in a [[2018\u201319 UEFA Nations League D]] game against [[Latvia national football team|Latvia]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[UEFA]]|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefanationsleague/season=2019/matches/round=2000959/match=2024060/index.html|title=Latvia v Kazakhstan game report|date=13 October 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n===Club===\n{{updated|match played 10 November 2019}}<ref>{{cite web|title=M.Fedin|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/maxim-fedin/273270/|website=soccerway.com|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=6 July 2017}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|valign=\"center\"|[[FK Spartak Subotica|Spartak Subotica]]\n|[[2015\u201316 Serbian SuperLiga|2015\u201316]]\n|valign=\"center\"|[[Serbian SuperLiga]]\n|5||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|-||6||0\n|-\n|valign=\"center\"|[[FC Atyrau|Atyrau]]\n|[[2016 FC Atyrau season|2016]]\n|valign=\"center\"|[[Kazakhstan Premier League]]\n|13||1||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|-||15||1\n|-\n|valign=\"center\"|[[FC Okzhetpes|Okzhetpes]]\n|[[2017 FC Okzhetpes season|2017]]\n|valign=\"center\"|[[Kazakhstan Premier League]]\n|26||2||2||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|-||28||3\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\" valign=\"center\"|[[FC Tobol|Tobol]]\n|[[2018 FC Tobol season|2018]]\n|rowspan=\"2\" valign=\"center\"|[[Kazakhstan Premier League]]\n|28||2||2||0||4||2||colspan=\"2\"|-||34||4\n|-\n|[[2019 FC Tobol season|2019]]\n|33||5||4||2||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||39||7\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!61!!7!!6!!2!!6!!2!!-!!-!!73!!11\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!105!!10!!11!!3!!6!!2!!-!!-!!122!!15\n|}\n\n===International===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!colspan=3|[[Kazakhstan national football team|Kazakhstan national team]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|2018||4||0\n|-\n|2019||8||1\n|-\n!Total||12||1\n|}\n''Statistics accurate as of match played 19 November 2019''<ref name=\"NFT Stats\">{{NFT player|pid=72205|name=Maksim Fedin|accessdate=20 November 2019}}</ref>\n\n===International goals===\n:''Scores and results list Kazakhstan's goal tally first.''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! No. !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n|align=center| 1. || 11 June 2019 || [[Astana Arena]], [[Nur-Sultan]], Kazakhstan || {{fb|SMR}} || align=center | '''2'''\u20130 || align=center | 4\u20130 || [[UEFA Euro 2020 qualifying Group I|UEFA Euro 2020 qualification]] \n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|maxim-fedin/273270}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150704221200/http://www.utakmica.rs/fudbaler/1365-fedin-maksim Maxim Fedin stats] at utakmica.rs\n* {{FootballDatabase.eu|246713}}\n* {{UEFA player|250056129}}\n\n{{FC Tobol squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fedin, Maxim}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Kazakhstani footballers]]